Taiwan's independence.

00:03:03.290 --> 00:03:04.590
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: Okay.

00:03:04.590 --> 00:03:05.890
&gt;&gt; Ha Jin: And, debated.

00:03:05.890 --> 00:03:07.190
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: All right.

00:03:07.190 --> 00:03:08.490
&gt;&gt; Ha Jin: Independence.

